stry is a teamwork. We are teammates, and for long term goal achievement & sustainability; no option is more appropriate than team. So, rather than throwing stones or passing balls; we should always adopt presentation policies. That’s for today. In Sha Allah will try to present something more in future. May Allah bless us & protect us.','','2020-04-29',1,NULL,NULL),(12,44,'Join our team','We are almost close the magic numbers of 5000\r\n\r\nMost of them are silent members ?? unfortunately \r\n\r\nApproximately almost 1 million executive are engaged in this Apparel and Textile industry of Bangladesh.. considering HR, Administration, Compliance, Merchandising & Marketing, Designe & Development, Commercial & Logistic , Production, Planning , I.E, Account/Finance, Maintenances, Quiality and Audit , Industrial Laundry etc \r\n\r\nWe can owned the industry if can stick together.. we can do betterment to the industry if we can stay together ..We can improve our Socio-Financial stays if hold our hands together...\r\n\r\nThe industry is suffering- its need your help and support \r\n\r\nLet’s build strong platform- to support the industry, support the industry and obviously ourselves...\r\n\r\n\r\nWe have started the initiatives ... and we need You to join with us ...','','2020-05-05',1,NULL,NULL);
